dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2014.[This dataset includes airports, locations of locks within the Fox Cities area, major highways, railroads and rustic roads within Outagamie County.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data was created to assist governmental agencies and other in making resource management decisions through the use of a Geographic Information System (GIS).]
